snippet.title: DarkStory Online Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Join to DarkStory Online!  Play Free Now on PC at http://www.darkstory2d.com 

Discover the magic world of DarkStory. Customize your own character, level up and defeat the most incredible creatures. Fly on a giant hawk, fight in the arena or race to the top of the ranking. In DarkStory, the game adapts to your playstyle - have fun!

Copyright © BraveWolf. All Rights Reserved
